Geographic data in this directory is derived from GeoNames
(https://www.geonames.org/), used under the Creative Commons Attribution 4.0
License (CC BY 4.0, https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/).

Source files (https://download.geonames.org/export/dump/):
  - cities15000.txt      → cities15000.tsv     (name, lat, lon, country code, admin1 code)
  - admin1CodesASCII.txt → admin1.tsv          (admin1 key → region name)
  - countryInfo.txt      → countries.tsv        (country code → country name, continent code)

The vendored files are compact projections of the above (selected columns only);
no GeoNames data was altered. © GeoNames, CC BY 4.0.
